responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "961A2DBC4AEDD789BE2F0FB7B73E04C9", "That-- yes. I think that\'s a sound plan. He had a pocket full of mushrooms and edible moss, so I believe his homestead must be nearby. That he lacks speech and carries dread in his eyes, though, I fear what you\'ll find.")
